{"id":"entities/great-wall","title":"Great Wall (Mutianyu)","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Great Wall</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Yahir hiked the Mutianyu section of the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/china\">Chinese</a> Great Wall on Nov 16, 2024 from <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/beijing\">Beijing</a>. Logistics: 80 yuan shuttle from Qianmen Exit C, 140 yuan via <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/alipay\">alipay</a> for entry + cable lift + slide back. First mentioned in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-11-26-beijinggg\">2024 11 26 beijinggg</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/beijing\">beijing</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/china\">china</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/alipay\">alipay</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-11-26-beijinggg\">2024 11 26 beijinggg</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/alipay","label":"AliPay"},{"id":"entities/beijing","label":"Beijing"},{"id":"summaries/2024-11-26-beijinggg","label":"BEIJINGGG — Beijing 4-day itinerary (Nov 2024)"},{"id":"entities/china","label":"China"},{"id":"lint-report","label":"Lint Report"},{"id":"summaries/2024-09-05-shanghai-sidequests","label":"Shanghai Sidequests — bucket list during the China chapter"}]}
